1
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:30,519
Lord Chancellor.

2
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:32,200
Why the panic?

3
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:33,359
What is it?

4
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,599
The Lingzhou gold mine

5
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,480
has been destroyed by Ning Chen.

6
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,040
What did you say?

7
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,319
Calm your anger, Lord Chancellor.

8
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:41,200
Luckily, Ning Chen acted on impulse

9
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:43,599
and killed Zhang Yuancang and the others.

10
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,560
Now there's no one left to testify,

11
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,599
so it shouldn't implicate you, Lord Chancellor.

12
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,519
After the Chongzhou case,

13
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,840
Lingzhou was our biggest source of income.

14
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:54,719
Without money,

15
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,519
how do I answer to those above?

16
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,480
How do I buy people's loyalty?

17
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,319
That bastard!

18
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,760
How dare he!

19
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,599
Lord Chancellor,

20
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:05,640
there's one more thing.

21
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,400
The moment I got the news,

22
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,639
I rushed to Ma Kaicheng's house,

23
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,080
but the Ma residence was empty.

24
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:14,639
Only a letter was left behind.

25
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,199
Read it.

26
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,439
Yes.

27
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:23,840
"Lord Left Chancellor,

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,599
I have taken Ma Kaicheng with me.

29
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,439
I hear that the Left Chancellor

30
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,479
and the Left Court King of Tuoluo

31
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:32,240
have been in close private contact.

32
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,919
I wonder if His Majesty knows of this.

33
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,280
Ning Chen has gone far to the northern frontier.

34
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,879
If he returns in triumph,

35
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,840
Ma Kaicheng will vanish without a trace.

36
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:45,759
But if anything happens to Ning Chen,

37
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,719
Ma Kaicheng will appear before His Majesty.

38
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:51,360
I urge the Left Chancellor to think carefully."

39
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,000
Lord Chancellor, please believe me,

40
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,800
this was certainly not my doing!

41
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,039
Just think,

42
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,919
if anything happened to you,

43
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,680
I would not escape death either.

44
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,159
He knows about our dealings with Tuoluo.

45
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:10,000
Who could it be?

46
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,879
From this day on,

47
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,400
spare no cost,

48
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,879
you must find this person.

49
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:17,759
Understood?

50
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:18,960
Yes.

51
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,199
And another thing,

52
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:23,719
tell our men at Beilin Pass

53
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,319
that Ning Chen must not

54
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,560
return alive.

55
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:28,960
Yes.

56
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,960
Haven't you eaten enough yet?

57
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,000
I'm just cold, that's all.

58
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:45,680
Still eating!

59
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,199
I didn't expect Beilin Pass

60
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,919
to be such a thriving place.

61
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,120
General Liang Jingwu, Guardian of the North,

62
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,879
is one of Great Xuan's fiercest generals.

63
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,639
They say

64
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,080
he was once under old General Chen.

65
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,199
No wonder.

66
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,120
A strong general breeds no weak soldiers.

67
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:00,520
Go on, go on.

68
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:01,560
Candied haws!

69
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,599
Have one.

70
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:05,599
I'm not having any.

71
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,639
You must be General Ning.

72
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,080
And you, sir, are?

73
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,199
Greetings, General Ning.

74
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,160
I am Liao Xingwen,

75
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,639
deputy general to General Liang.

76
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,519
General Liang sent me to receive you.

77
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,959
Thank you, Deputy General Liao.

78
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,639
Take me to see General Liang.

79
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,839
General Ning, this way please.

80
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,000
General Ning Chen, reporting to General Liang.

81
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:41,360
Greetings, General Liang.

82
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:43,480
General Ning, no need for such formalities.

83
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,399
You're the Northern Expedition General appointed by His Majesty.

84
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,759
Though we share the same rank,

85
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,240
His Majesty has decreed

86
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:51,160
that you lead, and I assist.

87
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:52,560
What qualifies him

88
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,319
to make our General his subordinate?

89
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,800
Probably some pampered brat from the capital,

90
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:57,720
here to build his prestige.

91
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,240
What a disgrace.

92
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,519
Say,

93
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,920
old General Chen sent me a letter

94
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,439
saying you're skilled in both arts and arms.

95
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,680
I've read your poetry.

96
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,560
Quite impressive indeed.

97
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:12,120
But how about your martial skills?

98
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:15,519
Care to spar with me?

99
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:19,079
He's trying to put me in my place.

100
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,120
Ning Chen.

101
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,399
General Liang commands all three armies.

102
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:23,920
His skills are beyond ordinary men.

103
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,959
Even I

104
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:25,920
am no match for him.

105
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,000
General Liang,

106
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,040
are you giving our Ning Chen a hard time?

107
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,480
If you'd rather not,

108
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:36,920
that's fine too.

109
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,000
General Liang.

110
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,560
After you.

111
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:00,120
General Ning truly excels in both arts and arms.

112
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,120
I'm thoroughly impressed.

113
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,399
He lost to me on purpose

114
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:04,800
to help establish my authority.

115
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,079
Could it be that old General Chen

116
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,399
asked him to look out for me?

117
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,399
General Liang,

118
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,360
you let me win.

119
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:15,759
A month ago,

120
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,800
the Left Court King sent ten thousand troops,

121
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,720
and I crushed them.

122
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,360
He must be short on manpower now,

123
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:22,240
so he's sending small cavalry units

124
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,240
to harass us repeatedly.

125
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:25,120
General Liang, are you certain

126
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:26,560
the Left Court King lacks troops?

127
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,000
The Tuoluo Kingdom has limited forces overall.

128
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:33,160
The Left Court King guards Tuoluo's southern border.

129
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,160
We've crossed paths many times before.

130
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:37,319
He has fifty thousand troops in total.

131
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,360
Last time I wiped out ten thousand,

132
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,360
and a few thousand fled.

133
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,240
According to intel I've received,

134
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,879
the Tuoluo dynasty redeployed thirty thousand troops.

135
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,879
So the Left Court King's current forces

136
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:47,920
should be fewer than twenty thousand.

137
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,920
But why would Tuoluo

138
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,199
pull thirty thousand troops from the Left Court King?

139
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,519
Tuoluo is warlike.

140
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,879
They don't only wage war against our Daxuan.

141
00:06:57,879 --> 00:07:00,959
Our scouts saw thirty thousand troops mobilize

142
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,800
and depart from the Left Court King's camp.

143
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:13,360
General Ning.

144
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,759
That's the camp of the Left Court King.

145
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:15,639
Yes.

146
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,360
Isn't he afraid we'll strike straight at his heart?

147
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,959
That valley has treacherous terrain.

148
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,920
We've suffered losses there before.

149
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,800
So we don't dare advance recklessly.

150
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,120
That's why we've been at a stalemate.

151
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,399
Thirty thousand troops have been pulled away,

152
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,639
yet their main camp hasn't retreated.

153
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,839
Chen, we're back.

154
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,279
How did the scouting go?

155
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,079
Those Tuoluo bastards.

156
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,839
Every time, it's all thunder and no rain.

157
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,439
They vanish before we can catch them.

158
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,199
Tell me about it.

159
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,240
Those refugees outside the city,

160
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,040
they're scared half to death.

161
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:50,639
Right now,

162
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,639
they're huddled at the foot of the city wall.

163
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,199
Homeless.

164
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,519
Pitiful.

165
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:56,879
Ning Chen.

166
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,199
General Liang has arrived.

167
00:07:58,839 --> 00:08:00,480
General Ning, you haven't left your tent for days.

168
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,839
Have you been studying the sand table?

169
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,639
Have you come up with a strategy?

170
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:04,279
General Liang,

171
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,040
I want to send out the troops.

172
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:09,800
Chen, are you insane?

173
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,399
In front of the Tuoluo camp,

174
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:14,600
the peaks on both sides

175
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,319
rise like blades piercing the sky.

176
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,959
Only the valley path lies between them,

177
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,959
easy to defend, hard to attack.

178
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,920
I've sent troops in before.

179
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,399
And because of that terrain,

180
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,319
they were ambushed,

181
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,480
suffering devastating losses.

182
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:30,000
I know you're eager to strike, General Ning,

183
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,199
but in war,

184
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:33,240
theory alone won't win battles.

185
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,320
General,

186
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,120
based on my analysis,

187
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,240
I'm certain that

188
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,639
within half a month,

189
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,799
a fierce battle is inevitable.

190
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,039
What do you mean by that?

191
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,840
Before I came here,

192
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,960
I met with old General Chen.

193
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,200
He told me

194
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,120
that Tuoluo's raids in past years

195
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,240
were never as severe as this year's.

196
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,600
Winter is almost here,

197
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,919
and the Left Court King is short on supplies.

198
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,799
They're sure to pull off something big.

199
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,039
You mean

200
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:03,159
their recent harassments

201
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,919
were meant to lull us into complacency?

202
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,720
Once,

203
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,200
twice,

204
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,759
and by the third, our guard fades.

205
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,879
Each time they send small cavalry units to harass us,

206
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,559
just minor skirmishes.

207
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,759
This makes our soldiers

208
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,279
underestimate the enemy

209
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,519
and let down their guard.

210
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:26,919
No wonder General Chen called you a born commander.

211
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,639
The old general's judgment

212
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:30,000
has never once been wrong.

213
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,320
You flatter me, General Liang.

214
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:33,799
General,

215
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,879
I have a plan.

216
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:47,559
My lord.

217
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:50,399
General Ning Chen from the capital requests an audience.

218
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:51,840
Let him wait.

219
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:53,000
My lord.

220
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:54,080
Is that wise?

221
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:57,200
I've heard of this Ning Chen.

222
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:59,039
A man of extraordinary talent.

223
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:02,399
Perhaps no one in this world can surpass him.

224
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,519
What a pity.

225
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,919
He offended the wrong people.

226
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,200
You may leave now.

227
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,000
Pay him no mind.

228
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,559
Let him wait two hours.

229
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,320
Yes, my lord.

230
00:10:15,879 --> 00:10:17,320
Such a pity.

231
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:21,240
Such a brilliant young man.

232
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:25,240
About to die on this frontier.

233
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,519
This Supervisor Kong puts on quite the airs.

234
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,360
Kong Yongchun is the Left Chancellor's man.

235
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:36,879
Naturally, he doesn't welcome us.

236
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:39,039
How do you know?

237
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,720
Forgetting what our Inspectorate does?

238
00:10:42,159 --> 00:10:42,879
Before coming here,

239
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,840
I reviewed the files

240
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,000
on every official stationed here.

241
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,039
Hurry, hurry!

242
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,120
Wonderful!

243
00:10:59,399 --> 00:10:59,840
Faster!

244
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:03,480
That must be Kong Yongchun's

245
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,960
worthless son.

246
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,919
And that must be Kong Yongchun's

247
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,240
wife, then.

248
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,440
Faster, faster!

249
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,399
Tired, are you?

250
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:17,440
Don't act rashly.

251
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,840
Hurry up, hurry up!

252
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,720
This is the frontier.

253
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,039
Life is the cheapest thing here.

254
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,200
Kong Yongchun.

255
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,279
He's the Supervisor here.

256
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,440
If we make an enemy of him,

257
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,000
he only needs to throw a few obstacles our way

258
00:11:28,679 --> 00:11:29,799
and we won't be able to move an inch.

259
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:32,960
Move it!

260
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,080
Faster!

261
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:36,960
Get running!

262
00:11:40,519 --> 00:11:42,120
A man like this calls himself Supervisor?

263
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,080
Corrupt swine.

264
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:48,879
Wonderful!

265
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,639
Will it never end?

266
00:12:00,919 --> 00:12:01,879
Still watching?

267
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,279
Let's go.

268
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,360
What are you grumbling about?

269
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,039
My lord, Ning Chen and his men have left.

270
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:15,679
What did you say?

271
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:18,000
He just left?

272
00:12:24,399 --> 00:12:26,559
Insolent brat!

273
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:31,840
General Liang.

274
00:12:32,399 --> 00:12:33,519
We proceed with the original plan.

275
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,480
How did your talks with Supervisor Kong go?

276
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,120
He cannot be told of this.

277
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:39,080
That breaks protocol.

278
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,279
Rules are rigid,

279
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:42,000
but men are not.

280
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,559
Our soldiers' lives hang in the balance.

281
00:12:47,679 --> 00:12:48,679
But he is the Supervisor.

282
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:49,799
Without his approval,

283
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,840
we cannot deploy any troops.

284
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,000
Fear not, General.

285
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,159
I bear the Imperial Sword from His Majesty.

286
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,240
To behold the Imperial Sword

287
00:12:57,519 --> 00:12:58,600
is to behold His Majesty himself.

288
00:12:59,240 --> 00:12:59,679
Old Gao.

289
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:00,240
Here.

290
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:02,720
You know what to do.

291
00:13:09,879 --> 00:13:10,440
Open the gates!

292
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:11,919
We'll split up.

293
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,080
General Liang,

294
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,759
you'll hold Beilin Pass.

295
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:15,879
Throw the gates wide open,

296
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:16,960
take in the refugees,

297
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,960
distribute gruel to lure the enemy.

298
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,000
Gao Ziping, maintain tight surveillance.

299
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:21,399
Keep your eyes on Kong Yongchun.

300
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,120
Not a word must leak out.

301
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:26,360
I'll lead the Musket Battalion lightly equipped,

302
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,759
cross over the canyon,

303
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:29,480
and strike straight to the heart!

304
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:44,159
General.

305
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:46,000
General Ning's prediction was right.

306
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,360
The enemy forces are at full strength,

307
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:48,720
over forty thousand men.

308
00:13:48,919 --> 00:13:50,360
They're advancing toward Beilin Pass.

309
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:53,799
Send word to all units.

310
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,960
Proceed as planned.

311
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:55,960
Stand ready for battle.

312
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:57,279
Yes, sir.

313
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,840
Ning, we've scouted it out.

314
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,240
Ahead lies the Left Court King's camp.

315
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,000
Just as you predicted,

316
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:06,320
fewer than a hundred guards.

317
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,679
Sons of Great Xuan!

318
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,240
The Tuoluo Kingdom's Zuodu army

319
00:14:16,759 --> 00:14:18,559
is locked in battle at Beilin Pass.

320
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,480
This is a heaven-sent chance.

321
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,720
We'll cut through the Zuodu royal court

322
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,159
and capture the Left Court King alive!

323
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:26,080
Since the founding of Great Xuan,

324
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,600
no one has fought this far.

325
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:29,639
Today,

326
00:14:30,519 --> 00:14:32,039
our names will be written in history.

327
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,440
Your families,

328
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,720
your sons and daughters,

329
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,240
will all be proud of you!

330
00:14:37,399 --> 00:14:38,039
Soldiers!

331
00:14:38,279 --> 00:14:38,840
Yes, sir!

332
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,600
We don't fight for ourselves,

333
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,320
we fight for our country,

334
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:46,519
for our children's children!

335
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,360
When the nation is safe,

336
00:14:49,399 --> 00:14:50,519
the people are safe.

337
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,720
What is a soldier's true grit?

338
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:56,679
The nerve to cut down any invader!

339
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,360
The will to fight to the death,

340
00:14:58,879 --> 00:15:00,240
to face death without fear!

341
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:01,519
Now,

342
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,200
with a great foe before us,

343
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,840
are you willing

344
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,519
to fight at my side?

345
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,440
We'll follow the General to the death!

346
00:15:08,799 --> 00:15:10,360
We'll follow the General to the death!

347
00:15:10,759 --> 00:15:12,360
We'll follow the General to the death!

348
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,080
Charge!

349
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:26,320
Charge!

350
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:27,440
Charge!

351
00:15:28,679 --> 00:15:30,120
Charge!

352
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:04,960
Left Court King!

353
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,200
Surrender now!

354
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,240
Who are you?

355
00:16:09,559 --> 00:16:10,320
Let me introduce myself.

356
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,320
The name's Ning Chen.

357
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,639
I'm here to take you down.

358
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,360
So you're Ning Chen.
